Uttar Pradesh
Dec 10, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			An eight-year-old girl was allegedly raped in Nidhauli Kala police station area here, police said today.

The girl, who had gone to an agriculture field to give lunch to her grandfather, was returning home when a youth living in the same police station area raped her yesterday, police said.

An FIR was registered by the father of the victim, employed in Delhi, today.

The girl has been sent for medical examination and efforts on to arrest the accused, police added.

